00:04:05.619 --> 00:04:07.979
As expected of Huanyue House's
finest courtesan queen.

00:04:07.980 --> 00:04:09.539
A beauty that stirs the heart.

00:04:10.287 --> 00:04:12.748
ظآزWe made a promise long agoظآز

00:04:12.749 --> 00:04:14.748
ظآزFor all our days to comeظآز

00:04:14.749 --> 00:04:18.411
ظآزYou are the fate I cannot outrunظآز

00:04:18.412 --> 00:04:21.019
ظآزHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?ظآز

00:04:21.020 --> 00:04:22.260
But no matter how beautiful,

00:04:24.659 --> 00:04:26.340
in their eyes,

00:04:27.539 --> 00:04:30.140
I am nothing more than a plaything.

00:04:32.940 --> 00:04:34.460
Beauty is not a sin.

00:04:35.460 --> 00:04:37.099
The ones who deserve punishment

00:04:37.580 --> 00:04:38.940
are them.

00:04:55.779 --> 00:04:57.059
This day

00:04:58.779 --> 00:05:00.780
is about to change.

00:05:10.979 --> 00:05:13.140
The Shengtang Guild's
assassins arrived quickly.

00:05:13.659 --> 00:05:14.499
Zhiyun.

00:05:14.539 --> 00:05:15.780
Stay behind me.

00:05:21.020 --> 00:05:22.140
Get back.

00:05:31.179 --> 00:05:33.340
Let none of them escape. Kill them all.

00:05:33.580 --> 00:05:34.419
Charge.

00:06:02.580 --> 00:06:03.780
Shanguan Yu!

00:06:04.060 --> 00:06:05.220
Go. Now.

00:06:36.659 --> 00:06:37.780
Shanguan Yu.

00:06:38.539 --> 00:06:39.659
Are you alright?

00:06:41.060 --> 00:06:42.499
Ruyan.

00:06:46.659 --> 00:06:48.380
I can only

00:06:50.339 --> 00:06:52.820
walk this road with you so far.

00:06:55.025 --> 00:06:57.306
You must walk

00:06:57.700 --> 00:07:00.539
the rest of the road on your own.

00:07:02.850 --> 00:07:05.179
No, Shanguan Yu.

00:07:05.820 --> 00:07:08.979
Did you not want
to see those villains punished?

00:07:09.219 --> 00:07:11.380
We are about to reach
the Court of Judicial Review.

00:07:12.179 --> 00:07:14.179
You cannot leave me halfway.

00:07:15.260 --> 00:07:16.539
Zhiyun.

00:07:19.219 --> 00:07:21.979
I do not know why,

00:07:23.060 --> 00:07:27.195
but I keep thinking
of our days in the thatched hut.

00:07:29.179 --> 00:07:31.099
Though life was hard,

00:07:32.900 --> 00:07:35.379
we were happy.

00:07:37.859 --> 00:07:40.419
But at that time,

00:07:40.659 --> 00:07:43.260
all I could think about was revenge.

00:07:47.225 --> 00:07:50.185
I left you there alone.

00:07:52.737 --> 00:07:54.819
ظآزStrangers meet again,
the past ablaze in vivid huesظآز

00:07:54.820 --> 00:07:56.059
I am sorry.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:03.279
ظآزA sharp arrow pierces through memoryظآز

00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:06.936
ظآزLonging spreads like inkظآز

00:08:06.937 --> 00:08:11.786
ظآزBeaded curtains divide love
and hate at either endظآز

00:08:11.787 --> 00:08:13.667
Do not say such nonsense.

00:08:14.137 --> 00:08:15.897
You will recover.

00:08:17.060 --> 00:08:18.460
We still have to

00:08:18.739 --> 00:08:20.140
avenge our wrongs together.

00:08:22.150 --> 00:08:23.910
And live a good life together.

00:08:25.150 --> 00:08:27.822
ظآزIn giving all, we found our only joyظآز

00:08:27.823 --> 00:08:31.462
ظآزThat year we laughed
beneath pear blossomsظآز

00:08:31.463 --> 00:08:34.962
ظآزOne night of snow
fell wild and restlessظآز

00:08:34.963 --> 00:08:41.899
ظآزEvery perfect ending
hides a trace of regretظآز

00:08:41.900 --> 00:08:45.399
ظآزWith blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewellظآز

00:08:45.400 --> 00:08:49.524
ظآزNo more longing will enter my dreamsظآز

00:08:49.525 --> 00:08:56.077
ظآزWhen all fades to drifting clouds,
may I share lasting peace with youظآز

00:09:24.675 --> 00:09:30.320
ظآزAfter endless sorrow endured
love is a word too hard to severظآز

00:09:31.575 --> 00:09:35.411
ظآزPast ties fade like a dream gone coldظآز

00:09:35.412 --> 00:09:38.084
ظآزIn giving all, we found our only joyظآز

