00:10:07.620 --> 00:10:09.739
Shanguan Yu.

00:10:16.125 --> 00:10:21.432
(The Court of Judicial Review)

00:10:22.020 --> 00:10:24.660
Hey, stop.

00:10:24.740 --> 00:10:25.538
What are you doing?

00:10:25.539 --> 00:10:26.379
Official,

00:10:26.380 --> 00:10:28.580
I have an urgent case to report.

00:10:28.939 --> 00:10:30.340
You?

00:10:30.939 --> 00:10:33.840
You are only a lone woman,
not a lady of rank.

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:35.760
What grounds do you have
to sound the drum for justice?

00:10:35.760 --> 00:10:37.458
Whatever it is, wait until dawn.

00:10:37.459 --> 00:10:38.418
This is improper.

00:10:38.419 --> 00:10:39.219
Official,

00:10:39.220 --> 00:10:40.739
I wish to accuse
Grand Commandant Gao Deng

00:10:40.740 --> 00:10:42.538
and Zhou Zihua of Huanyue House.

00:10:42.539 --> 00:10:44.640
They colluded in secret,
trafficking courtesans,

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:45.920
and treating lives as worthless.

00:10:46.020 --> 00:10:46.938
I beg you for mercy.

00:10:46.939 --> 00:10:48.660
Please allow me
to beat the drum for justice.

00:10:49.659 --> 00:10:51.538
Petty disputes among brothel women,

00:10:51.539 --> 00:10:53.458
are worth you coming all this way?

00:10:53.459 --> 00:10:54.339
Go on.

00:10:54.340 --> 00:10:55.739
Do not defile this place.

00:10:56.380 --> 00:10:58.060
I beg you, Official.

00:10:59.020 --> 00:11:00.540
You woman,

00:11:00.659 --> 00:11:02.139
why will you not listen?

00:11:02.620 --> 00:11:04.180
(Is there truly)

00:11:04.459 --> 00:11:07.060
(no place in this world that
will grant justice to women like us?)

00:11:07.479 --> 00:11:08.818
(How many lives cry out in misery?)

00:11:08.819 --> 00:11:09.680
Are you leaving or not?

00:11:09.680 --> 00:11:11.460
(How many wronged souls cannot rest?)

00:11:11.539 --> 00:11:13.080
If you do not leave now,
I truly will have you locked up.

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:14.380
- (I refuse to believe it.)
- Leave now!

00:11:14.387 --> 00:11:15.895
(The Court of Judicial Review)

00:11:35.380 --> 00:11:37.779
Oh no, what are we going to do?

00:11:38.220 --> 00:11:39.340
This...

00:11:39.740 --> 00:11:40.859
This...

00:11:41.459 --> 00:11:44.779
(The Court of Judicial Review)
Fire! Fire!